pt.ptcris

Class PTCRISyncResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • pt.ptcris.PTCRISyncResult

  • public final class PTCRISyncResult
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that encapsulates the result of the synchronization procedures for a particular work. Currently only the export methods report these results.
